How to Create a Simple Repository

Create an account.
Open Menu & Go to -----> Repositories -----> Click “New Repository”
Create a repository name -----> “ITEC65_YourSurnames”
Set description -----> “This a step-by-step guide on how to create a simple repository.”
Go to Configuration -----> Set: Visibility (Public), README (On), License (MIT)

